{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Blue Hunter is a roguelike deckbuilding game with RPG elements. Fight monsters and revive them, level up, choose your stats, create your deck of undead monsters, beat gods and become the almighty god!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dynamic stats: Choose which stats to increase with each level up. Create your own playstyle!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992190/extras/stat_customization.gif?t=1736457881\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Strategic sacrifices: Are you ready to go through hell? Make sacrifices in order to get stronger. Only pain awaits you!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992190/extras/dual_class_system.gif?t=1736457881\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An ever changing army: You can revive all the monsters you kill to assist you in battle as cards. Your deck is always unique!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992190/extras/monster_resurrection.gif?t=1736457881\" /></p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Warrior's Triumph","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2992190/a6202db01bdf9bff738adbe40be1508c17997278.jpg"},{"name":"Bringer Of Calamity","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2992190/59ded7ca2d40b7e4f7c0b201f3525d0aca67ceed.jpg"},{"name":"Crusher Conqueror","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2992190/b0b34e20e8f273bd26dce3584f30078fcb6b17bb.jpg"},{"name":"Overwhelming Power","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2992190/d61a938830cdb1b9c4dbcba